{"tid":1562114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在街上，聽到警察一家的對話","createTime":"2019-09-12T01:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T01:38:33.000Z","uid":264104,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6939f04370907c1a10dfcc19d25b7cf50c076d95","tid":1562114,"uid":264104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:35:15.000Z","msg":"返工期間，聽到一家人既對話：<br />\n有個拎住燈籠既細路好好奇咁講：<br />\n頭先果隻咩曱甴黎架，俾我睇下，俾我睇下！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問左幾聲，個男人都唔出聲，之後個女人就好大聲講：你好煩呀，人講你就信。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細路就冇講野，而我又行開左。<br />\n<br />\n隔左幾廿秒，先恍然大悟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果家係警察一家(附近有警察宿舍), 因為預左中秋冇假放，要預早同屋企人提早過中秋。<br />\n之後應該個男人，見到有d人，話佢地曱甴同影相。之後就發生我聽到既對答了。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">講咁多野，我只想問d mon住連登既差佬，<br />\n你講到你自已咁正義，你敢唔敢將，你地做既野講俾你細路聽呀？你派臥底屈示威者，強姦，放火，殺人！</span></strong><br />\n你點教你d小朋友，咩係勇氣，同是非黑白呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返份工姐，返到你咁。<br />\n回頭啦。<br />\n俾你細路大個左，知道你做過既野，你依家做既一切都冇哂用架啦。<br />\n<br />\n你既未來唔係喺同事手上，喺係你下一代同屋企人手上呀！"},{"pid":"0e517af6a21b6da431324827d0dcefee58e98f18","tid":1562114,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:35:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.